Grab one of our hand poured candles while they last: https://wildrootscafeco.com/collections/candles
*Limited supplies- family made*

Our candles are made with the highest quality materials on the market and hand-poured carefully in the shop. We use eco-friendly soy wax, cotton core wicks, and the finest quality oils. They are lead free, phthalate free, paraffin free, and dye free. Soy candles burn incredibly clean and slow while throwing a wonderful scent for hours! We use the maximum amount of scent the wax can hold so you'll be sure to have a great smelling candle.  

In today's video we work to tie the wood portion of our A-Frame Addition together with the block safe room.  We battle severe swings in weather and move into our new hand poured candle and soap facility to begin large scale production in small town West Virginia.
